snippet.title: KILL YOUR FRIENDS - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/675110/KILL_YOUR_FRIENDS/

KILL YOUR FRIENDS is a frantic arena shooter for up to 6 players. Play solo, or battle your pals online. Grab a weapon, don your comically oversized hat & an absurdly mismatched outfit, and KILL YOUR FRIENDS!

Coming to Steam in April 2022!
